Maddy ?

5
00:00:33,900 --> 00:00:35,000
Salut, Michael.

6
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:37,400
Je voulais te demander quelque chose.

7
00:00:38,300 --> 00:00:39,700
A propos du bal de la St Valentin.

8
00:00:39,900 --> 00:00:40,700
Oui ?

9
